desc_long							评测						“Pixel Star is a pure arcade game about wielding ridiculous amounts of firepower...”Hardcore Gamer												关于这款游戏							Pixel Star embodies arcade philosophy; brutally challenging, fun and rewarding. With a focus on progressively intense fast-paced action, player freedom, and solid gameplay, Pixel Star reimagines the shoot-em-up genre. From black holes to space centipedes, nebula storms to stray satellites, there is always something new to discover.Features: Loads of power-ups and customization options Unique, varied enemy AI Merciless boss battles Progressive difficulty and intensity Open-space environment Gorgeous particle effects						
